{"tid":1655913,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"急急急推 草菅人命啦 比Uniqlo 更慘","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:39:14.000Z","uid":243309,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2e964e699e7c4fa75dfe7a50c205bfcf3af621","tid":1655913,"uid":243309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"本人係onitsuka tiger職員，因為黨鐵今個月不斷早收，所以住係九龍同新界既同事而工作於銅鑼灣係非常唔方便，返屋企時間比平時遲超過1個半鐘，公司不但冇體諒職員，而且冇任何津貼幫我哋，我見Uniqlo都已經有應有既待遇，我哋已頂唔順，以下係罪證，希望比大家公審<br />\n<br />\n罪證1:<span style=\"color: gold;\">其他舖頭早收哂，得返我哋獨市！</span><br />\n因為呢幾個月有好多公眾活動，所以係京士頓街所有舖頭都開一個gp，目的想知所有舖頭會幾點落閘，<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個月黨鐵不斷早落閘，成條京士頓街舖頭都講明會係黨鐵落閘前一個至半鐘落閘比大家走，於是就cap圖比公司阿頭知，結果一係唔覆，一係就話正常時間22:00落閘，個個同事返屋企要等1個半鐘車，仲要行返屋企，每日如是</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4hTSDX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4hTSDX.png&h=1c826941&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbPrtc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbPrtc0.png&h=7a431554&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCR5JM4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCR5JM4.png&h=11f60fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/175703_3598c89179b3898ac436c5735523b985.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F175703_3598c89179b3898ac436c5735523b985.png&h=8d8a2019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/175910_2a3106da6e4790f534734c499ac028c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F175910_2a3106da6e4790f534734c499ac028c0.png&h=ad7c0196&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/180039_9279983cd739e519752dbe204f1c4b91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F180039_9279983cd739e519752dbe204f1c4b91.png&h=7a98b66f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/180238_40d827439fb88802a3ba07f25b99f56b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F180238_40d827439fb88802a3ba07f25b99f56b.png&h=875b1ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/15/180432_ea8f078a6a3805b92c44f9d94eeeb94f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F180432_ea8f078a6a3805b92c44f9d94eeeb94f.png&h=cd54b87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪證2:<span style=\"color: gold;\">已讀不回，就算應都好串，串我哋拎著數</span><br />\n每次有公眾活動進行，有舖頭落閘，我哋就會即刻匯報比上司聽，等佢作決定，但係10次有8次都係已讀不回，我哋不知所措，其他公事搞爛gag秒回，一講早收就潛水，就算應都係串我哋拎著數<br />\n<br />\n罪證3: <span style=\"color: gold;\">冇得cam返的士錢</span><br />\n正常時間22:00收工，有好多同事係住比較遠既地方，巴士小巴返唔到屋企，冇黨鐵搭係非常唔方便既事，個個排巴士小巴要等成1個半鐘先上到車，同上司反映改黨鐵落閘前半個至一個鐘走，唔理我哋，冇車返屋企唔理，於是就講搭的士有冇得cam返，又已讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾日本公司唔理前線員工，淨係顧住自己盤生意唔想虧咁，每晚返到屋企12點幾，本來40分鐘車程變2個鐘，搞到我哋收工勁辛苦，我琴晚終於頂唔順等左1個鐘都冇車，頂唔順搭的士，諗住係gp講會有好既回應可以cam錢，結果已讀不回。希望各位巴絲打推post，比更加多人知，如果其他人有同樣問題，一定要發聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e65f50e6fa51247c765300746aaf5015a08e16ad","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫推.推到公司高層出黎面對</span>"},{"pid":"1d0a266e70d0da550eb0fdf4021867ada636f567","tid":1655913,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"草管人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85765ed603371ba8dd43f0af201ce74e8d6c83f6","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出黎面對</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0972602f7909c414107ff86979c992e3bfb2d8a4","tid":1655913,"uid":164591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街"},{"pid":"00351236da6861d5ccc57a29234279ebe59b9c02","tid":1655913,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b07c8f30a68d5e57e78197df79df3268dc4952","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"本人都是該公司員工.<br />\n<br />\n我地全店上上下下都係黃絲<br />\n有時想因爲黨鐵封站 <br />\n附近所有商店都己經關門<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唯獨得返我地.依然獨市.全條街所有人都走曬<br />\n另外信息都已告知上層.但係佢地都只係己讀不會<br />\n希望大家幫手推到佢地出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1759515eb1d6fc4bc8f93b0485ff040aae4861ab","tid":1655913,"uid":281972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4f6a072550f00f8d7431400c68f129c9ea1b2de","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e04d59fc97941f3d7427c4876dd223de6364ae52","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"要比更加多人知道"},{"pid":"e8ffb3ea5017826b96075332ac3f5d1d15441482","tid":1655913,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"幫公司裝修"},{"pid":"80277cef2fa34f2b80da0abf299eb44020d79aba","tid":1655913,"uid":243309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"要用自己補鐘走去趕搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c0fa810f01d20cd7247e620ae94ed2311f4350","tid":1655913,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"運動家黎。"},{"pid":"76f1a75f0d977d571b0ab2f128a0037a095d55ae","tid":1655913,"uid":243309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c0fa810f01d20cd7247e620ae94ed2311f4350","tid":1655913,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"運動家黎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"唔係運動家架，直營店黎"},{"pid":"02b1eadf2b94d29ebb9e9f8961b62d71f395f477","tid":1655913,"uid":243309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"今日onitsuka tiger 又獨市啦。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />7點幾到依家都冇開單，隔離Adidas都走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yjSpWH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yjSpWH.jpg&h=673d2845&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvOWRBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvOWRBJ.jpg&h=94dd865c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c9271544b43ee75c761956219eefccfd84675e9","tid":1655913,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"公司太無良喎"},{"pid":"163a852a4557a23a3fbc20949e1c81071cf76afa","tid":1655913,"uid":54248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"出面都冇人仲要開門"},{"pid":"b6b21279a378c86988f91e5c10b927e11f95b90c","tid":1655913,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bd5b454552011176355bfb8f3d97f568a114e9","tid":1655913,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50fc28557c3880b80bc999174b250ff2533f915","tid":1655913,"uid":5264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"要屌 推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"5c8e12ef1f431e1db472d0cbad15305ca78b299e","tid":1655913,"uid":298622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"其實都唔會有人嚟買衫㗎啦而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早啲收舖收工唔係更加可以止蝕咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ni mean冷氣 燈之類費用 都係要俾錢交㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fddb0738dacf9778ad76b59e46fe4b6e4456b83","tid":1655913,"uid":38609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩呀<br />\n夠薑就罷撚左工先出黎開post啦<br />\n要人地做埋你個份呀?<br />\n又唔敢罷工 已經夠晒忙 仲要做幾多條支線任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cabe9c78201cb904000f379476c1da25fca8fb5","tid":1655913,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"呢d良心公司嚟，唔幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f4e040f96bdd69b7516300a15dc5e3610544cf","tid":1655913,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"連名都唔敢開"},{"pid":"6b60a98d0fa09a470a21a6d8fc089f2175739ea2","tid":1655913,"uid":13174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"}]}